# GumBot Privacy Policy

**Effective Date:** January 17, 2026

GumBot (ID: 1458462560507527352) is a free multipurpose Discord bot operated by [FireDevelopment]. By inviting or using GumBot, you agree to this Privacy Policy.

## 1. Data We Collect
We collect minimal data needed for features:
- Discord user IDs and usernames (for leveling, warnings)
- Server IDs and basic settings (prefixes, welcome channels)
- XP/levels data (stored per user ID per server)
- No message content is stored permanently (transient for anti-spam if enabled)
- No emails, IP addresses, or personal contact info

## 2. How We Use Data
- Provide core bot functions (moderation, music, XP, tickets)
- Improve bot features and fix bugs
- We do not sell, rent, or use data for advertising

## 3. Data Storage & Security
- Stored securely on private servers (JSON/SQLite files)
- Access restricted to bot owner
- Reasonable security measures in place, but no 100% guarantee

## 4. Data Sharing
- Shared only with Discord API as required
- No third-party sharing except legal requirements

## 5. Your Rights
- Request view/delete of your data (contact via support server)
- Data deleted when bot leaves your server or on request

## 6. Changes
We may update this policy â€” continued use means acceptance.

## 7. Contact
